cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is about image segmentation, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves integrating different techniques such as Parzen-Rosenblatt window method, non-local weights entropy, and regularizer of phase field, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also includes numerical experiments, which may fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) categories.
